title: League of Legends Epic Jazz Video

embed.description: Hi, Everyone I come to you with a Jazz video, short and sweet sorry I have been away I have been working on a Rap video which hopefully will come out soon. Trying to get 1 video a week done but depends on amount of work I have.

body: This is the second time I have shared one of his videos with you all, but I love them so much and he deserves  more views for these funny vids.  Not sure what you guys think? But I think he is pretty good.
